name: Terminalius Maximus
description: The $BARON project is a community-driven token aiming to establish a dynamic ecosystem with innovative applications. While currently focused on building a strong foundation and growing its community, the project is actively developing a mini-game that will integrate with the $BARON token, creating an engaging use case and driving user interaction. The goal is to evolve $BARON into a token with real engagement and utility, with future plans to expand its applications as the ecosystem grows.
